To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private TasukiGap _tasukigap;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_tasukigap = TasukiGap(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_tasukigap.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "tasukigap", _tasukigap.Current.Value);
}
